458
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,420
that her bathroom had traces of my life,

459
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,220
that's pretty normal.

460
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,980
Charlie's room does too.

461
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:16,420
His cabinet even has my towel in it.

462
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:33,700
You've really thought this through.

463
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:36,490
But that's alright.

464
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,250
The night is still long.

465
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,900
