talking behind closed doors.

521
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:24,300
Why shouldn't I be told those secrets?

522
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:25,780
I'm just an outsider, right?

523
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,820
Have you noticed

524
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,490
any unusual details about their life?

525
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,380
Mr. Liang, what would you call

526
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:43,780
an unusual detail?

527
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,780
Are they close in daily life?

528
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:48,460
Close? Of course they're close.

529
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:49,650
Yes.

530
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:50,530
Before his wife came,

531
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:54,170
Mr. Lee's meals, sleep,
even bathroom visits,

532
00:37:54,190 --> 00:37:55,530
were all taken care of by me, right?

533
00:37:55,550 --> 00:37:57,380
I was with him all the time.

534
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:58,610
Then things changed.

535
00:37:58,630 --> 00:38:00,570
Once his wife arrived,
I was like furniture.

536
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,130
Do they argue often?

537
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:04,300
Argue? Of course they do.

538
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,460
One's from here, one's from abroad.

539
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:08,130
Their values are just different.

540
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:10,570
What time do they usually
sleep and wake?

541
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,380
That's not very consistent.

542
00:38:12,630 --> 00:38:15,530
Usually, Mrs. Lee goes to bed
and gets up early.

543
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:16,860
While Mr. Lee works,

544
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:19,260
I follow his schedule,
staying up and sleeping in.

545
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:21,090
Director Lee has a brain condition.

546
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:22,530
When his illness flares up,

547
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:25,050
does it disturb Mrs. Lee's rest?

548
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,820
Mr. Liang,

549
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,740
the things you're asking me about

550
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,490
are all what happens
behind closed doors.

551
00:38:33,510 --> 00:38:35,090
How would I know, right?

552
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,980
What if I really need to know?

553
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,820
Mr. Liang, let me think a bit more.

554
00:39:06,110 --> 00:39:07,530
Let me think again.

555
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,260
Just be honest

556
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:53,420
and God will bless you.

557
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,530
Fine, I'll tell you the truth.

558
00:39:58,550 --> 00:40:00,570
They never lived under the same roof.

559
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,050
How do you know that?

560
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:08,380
Mr. Lee is a Christian.

561
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:10,820
Before marriage,
he'd never slept with his wife.

562
00:40:10,840 --> 00:40:12,610
He's always sharing a room with me.

563
00:40:13,150 --> 00:40:14,460
But you know, stuff like this…

564
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,610
You can't really tell anyone.

565
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,980
I mean, all the neighbors think

566
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,380
they're madly in love.

567
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,740
So why don't they live together?

